How to use ESang wifi treadmill 

1、ESang treadmill T4000 device link : https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/Home-use-Electric-Folding-Treadmill-Low_62546318946.html?spm=a2700.wholesale.deiletai6.13.685f53118VTIMJ 
ESang Treadmill info : Brand Name: ESANG, Model Number: T4000, Product Name:T4000 plus Mini Treadmill.

2、Download Forrest App, iOS version On Apple AppStore, Android version on Google play. 

3、Open the Forrest app and create an account. Forrest app find the path "Mine - IoT config" , follow network configure direction, step by step to finish the ESang Treadmill network configure. 

4、Alexa controll the ESang Treadmill T4000 order :
Alexa,Turn on the treadmill;
Alexa,Turn off the treadmill ;
Alexa,Speed up;
Alexa,make it faster;
Alexa,Speed down;
Alexa,Set the speed to 5; 
Alexa,Set the treadmill;
Alexa,speed to 5;
Alexa,set the treadmill speed to 3.

